---
layout: default
permalink: /index.html
title: JSON Meta Application Protocol Specification (JMAP)
description: >-
    JMAP is the open protocol that replaces IMAP (and CardDAV and CalDAV). It’s
    faster, simpler, more powerful, and built for how email works today.
stylesheets:
    - home
scripts:
    - home
get_started:
    eyebrow: Get started
    title: Up and running in minutes
    cards:
        -
            title: Discover the endpoint
            body: >-
                Fetch <code>/.well-known/jmap</code> for the session object - capabilities,
                accounts, and all API URLs.
        -
            title: Authenticate
            body: >-
                Standard OAuth 2.0 or Bearer tokens. No custom auth protocol to
                implement. Works with what you already have.
        -
            title: Make your first call
            body: >-
                POST a <code>methodCalls</code> array. Query, fetch, and send, all in one
                HTTP request.
        -
            title:  Subscribe to push
            body: >-
                Open an EventSource connection. Your UI stays current without
                polling. All mailboxes, instantly.
explore:
    eyebrow: Explore
    title: Where to next?
    cards:
        -
            href: /why-jmap/
            eyebrow: Make the case
            title: Why JMAP?
            body: >-
                The technical and practical argument for replacing IMAP,
                grounded in Fastmail's benchmarks and real implementation
                experience.
        -
            href: /spec/
            eyebrow: Specifications and Guides
            title: Read the spec
            body: >-
                The full JMAP protocol &mdash; core (RFC 8620), mail (RFC 8621),
                contacts, calendars &mdash; plus client and server guides.
        -
            href: /software/
            eyebrow: Software and Libraries
            title: Find implementations
            body: >-
                Services with JMAP support, client libraries, server
                implementations, and more.

---
<section class='hero hero--landing u-wrapper'>
    <div class='hero__inner'>
        <h1 class='hero__h1 u-text-jumbo u-font-bold u-kerning-tight'>
            The API for
            <span class='hero__accent'>better email</span>
        </h1>
        <p class='hero__sub u-text-lg'>
            {{ page.description }}
        </p>
        <div class='hero__links'>
            <a href='{{ site.baseurl }}/why-jmap/' class='button button--standard u-text-sm'>Why JMAP?</a>
            <a href='{{ site.baseurl }}/spec/' class='button button--standard u-text-sm'>Explore the spec</a>
            <a href='{{ site.baseurl }}/software/' class='button button--standard u-text-sm'>Find apps and libraries</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class='bento u-wrapper'>
    <div class='bento__card bento__card--push'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>
                {% include icons/pulse.liquid class='u-sq-12' %}
                <span>Real-time push</span>
            </div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                Instant updates.<br>
                Zero overhead.
            </div>
            <div class='bento__card-body u-text-sm'>
                Get instant push via EventSource &mdash; one connection, all mailboxes. Or use WebPush for
                mobile-compatible push, no permanent connection required.
            </div>
            <div class='u-flex-spacer'></div>
            <div class='push-tl'>
                <span class='push-name'>JMAP push</span>
                <div class='push-track' id='push-track-j'>
                    <div class='push-dot push-dot--j' id='push-dot-j'></div>
                </div>
                <span class='push-time push-time--j' id='push-t-j'>&lt;1s</span>
                <span class='push-name'>IMAP polling</span>
                <div class='push-track' id='push-track-i'>
                    <div class='push-dot push-dot--i' id='push-dot-i'></div>
                </div>
                <span class='push-time push-time--i' id='push-t-i'>30s+</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--battery'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>Mobile battery life</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                Efficiency that<br>
                <i>matters</i>.
            </div>
            <div class='stat-num u-text-2xl u-font-bold'>2&ndash;3&times;</div>
            <div class='bento__card-sub u-text-xs'>
                better than IMAP<br>
                measured on real devices
            </div>
            <div class='batt-row'>
                <div>
                    <div class='batt-wrap'>
                        <div class='batt-shell'>
                            <div class='batt-fill batt-fill--accent' id='bf-jmap'></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class='batt-tip batt-tip--teal'></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='batt-lbl'>JMAP</div>
                </div>
                <div style='margin-left:10px'>
                    <div class='batt-wrap'>
                        <div class='batt-shell'>
                            <div
                                class='batt-fill batt-fill--muted'
                                id='bf-imap'
                            ></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class='batt-tip batt-tip--muted'></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='batt-lbl'>IMAP</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--bench'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>Performance</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                Rock solid sync.<br>
                Every time.
            </div>
            <div class='bento__card-body u-text-sm'>
                Sync changes more easily, more efficiently, and much, much faster. A single HTTP roundtrip is often all
                that's required.
            </div>
            <div class='u-flex-spacer'></div>
            <div class='bench-bars' id='bench-bars'>
                <div class='bench-row bench-row--jmap'>
                    <span class='bench-lbl'>JMAP</span>
                    <div class='bench-track'><div class='bench-fill'></div></div>
                    <span class='bench-val'>13.1 KB</span>
                </div>
                <div class='bench-row bench-row--tb'>
                    <span class='bench-lbl'>T&rsquo;bird</span>
                    <div class='bench-track'><div class='bench-fill'></div></div>
                    <span class='bench-val'>2.9 MB</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='bench-detail u-text-xs'>
                Bandwidth used when resyncing after restart on a mailbox with 28,234 messages.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--json'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>Standard HTTP + JSON</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                Deployment<br>
                made easy.
            </div>
            <div class='bento__card-body u-text-sm'>
                JMAP works natively with existing infrastructure like nginx, Cloudflare, WAFs, load balancers, and DDoS
                protection — no specialist IMAP tooling required. And it works just as great for webmail as native
                clients.
            </div>
            <div class='hs'>
                <div class='hs-layer hs-app u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>JMAP for Mail</div>
                <div class='hs-layer hs-jmap u-text-xs'>JMAP Core</div>
                <div class='hs-layer hs-json u-text-xs'>JSON</div>
                <div class='hs-layer hs-http u-text-xs'>HTTP / TLS</div>
            </div>
            <div class='u-flex-spacer'></div>
            <div class='http-request'>
                <span class='http-request__method'>POST /jmap/api</span>
                <div class='http-request__status'>
                    <div class='http-request__status-dot'></div>
                    <span class='http-request__status-label'>connected</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--rfc'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>RFC</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>An open IETF standard.</div>
            <p class='bento__card-body u-text-sm'>
                No patents. No fees. Fully documented. JMAP is an open standard any organisation can implement, not more
                proprietary lock-in from big tech companies.
            </p>
            <div class='bento__card-links'>
                <a
                    href='{{ site.baseurl }}/spec/'
                    class='button button--cta u-text-sm'
                    target='_blank'
                    rel='noopener'
                    >Read the spec</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--spec'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>Spec complexity</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                So. Much.<br>
                Simpler.
            </div>
            <div class='stat-num u-text-2xl u-font-bold'>5&times;</div>
            <div class='bento__card-sub u-text-xs'>
                smaller than IMAP<br>
                51k vs 272k words
            </div>
            <div class='doc-bars'>
                <div class='doc-bar-row'>
                    <span class='doc-bar-lbl'>JMAP</span>
                    <div class='doc-bar-track'>
                        <div class='doc-bar-fill doc-bar-jmap'></div>
                    </div>
                    <span class='doc-bar-val doc-bar-val--accent'>51k</span>
                </div>
                <div class='doc-bar-row'>
                    <span class='doc-bar-lbl'>IMAP</span>
                    <div class='doc-bar-track'>
                        <div class='doc-bar-fill doc-bar-imap'></div>
                    </div>
                    <span class='doc-bar-val doc-bar-val--muted'>272k</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='bento__card bento__card--lang'>
        <div class='bento__card-wrapper'>
            <div class='bento__card-label u-text-xs u-font-semibold'>Running code</div>
            <div class='bento__card-title u-text-lg u-font-bold'>
                A fast-growing<br>
                ecosystem.
            </div>
            <div class='lang-chips'>
                <span class='lang-chip'>Webmail</span>
                <span class='lang-chip'>Rust library</span>
                <span class='lang-chip'>iOS app</span>
                <span class='lang-chip'>Server</span>
                <span class='lang-chip'>Typescript library</span>
                <span class='lang-chip'>Terminal client</span>
            </div>
            <div class='u-flex-spacer'></div>
            <div>
                <a href='{{ site.baseurl }}/software/' class='button button--outline button--sm u-text-sm'
                    >Find implementations &rarr;</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class='section section--alt'>
    <div class='u-wrapper'>
        <span class='section__label u-text-sm u-font-semibold'>
            {{- page.get_started.eyebrow -}}
        </span>
        <h2 class='section__h2 u-text-3xl u-font-bold'>
            {{- page.get_started.title -}}
        </h2>
        <ol class='get-started__grid'>
            {% for card in page.get_started.cards %}
                <li class='card get-started__card'>
                    <h3 class='card__title u-font-bold'>{{ card.title }}</h3>
                    <p class='card__body u-text-sm'>{{ card.body }}</p>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ol>
    </div>
</section>

<section class='section section--accent'>
    <div class='u-wrapper'>
        <span class='section__label u-text-sm u-font-semibold'>Explore</span>
        <h2 class='section__h2 u-text-3xl u-font-bold'>Where to next?</h2>
        <ul class='card-grid'>
            {% for card in page.explore.cards %}
                <li>
                    {%
                        include components/link-card.liquid
                        href=card.href
                        eyebrow=card.eyebrow
                        title=card.title
                        body=card.body
                    %}
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
